snippet.textDisplay: I am always contented, when Lebron James and his assistants win a bb game.  Of course, I fervently CONGRATULATE whichever team in which he participates so gallantly.  It goes without saying that he is my FAVORITE basketball player.  However, whatever the flaws that allow an almost 40-point lead to be so quickly diminished by the Suns must be contemplated and efforts must be put into action to avoid them. On this  very premise, I offer a very high degree of encomium to the SUNS. My big measure of ADMIRATION for Kelly Oubre Jr! He is fearless, pugnacious and is able to emanate a great deal of charm. May ALL the PLAYERS enjoy enduring HAPPINESS and HEALTH through the NEW year, 2020!
